# Always run unit tests after changes

After any code change in this repo, run the unit tests before finishing:

```powershell
python tests/test_digest_checkin.py
```

- Do this automatically — do not wait for the user to ask.
- Fix failures before considering the change done.
- Only use `--live` when the user explicitly wants a real email sent.
